Unable to get stock devian squeeze amd64 virtualbox 3.2.10-dfsg-1,
on UAA ITS WebApps debian squeeze amd64 boothite workstation, to 
accept a windows 7 x64 install.  Punching up to virtualbox 4.0.8
from virtualbox.org/


1. Downloaded virtualbox-4.0_4.0.8-71778-Debian-squeeze_amd64.deb
from virtualbox.org/

2. Uninstalled virtual box 3.2.10-dfsg-1:
# aptitude remove virtualbox-ose virtualbox-ose-dkms virtualbox-ose-qt 
